                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 ml-14">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-800 dark:text-green-300 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Sensor Fusion</span>
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Rehabilitation</span>
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Feedback Systems</span>
                  </div>
